<div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-sm-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">The Money </h2>
        <p class="lead">We rely completely on donations made on this site.</p>
        <p>We have calculated that it costs about $1,200 to put a girl through secondary school. Once we have collected that money, we keep it until the beginning of the Zambian school year (January). We will pay for one school year at a time in case the girl is unable to finish school. We send the money directly to the school's bank account to minimize fraud. </p>
        <p>Any excess money from over donation or girls who don’t finish school will rolled over to help a different girl. </p>
    </div>
